    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Radiometric dating method which measures the age of igneous calcium carbonate materials. The technique calculates the degree to which radioactive thorium-230 isotopes within a sample have reestablished secular equilibrium with their parent uranium-234 isotopes.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>English</Note_Language>
